ll generate a puzzle for it, from thousands of possibilities!<br></li><li>Collection mode to view your discoveries<br></li><li>Replay to beat your best time on any puzzle<br></li><li>13 Achievements<br></li><li>How To Play mode to teach you the basics</li></ul>",
